# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:15
translate spanish reba0_508c504c:

    # "I drive away down the street, not really sure exactly where I want to go yet."
    "Me alejo por la calle, sin saber muy bien aún adónde quiero ir."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:16
translate spanish reba0_1e1676b6:

    # "I start down the backroads, feeling reminiscent. These are the roads that my dad always drove down to avoid the traffic through the middle of the town."
    "Empiezo a recorrer las carreteras secundarias, sintiéndome nostálgico. Son las carreteras por las que mi padre siempre conducía para evitar el tráfico del centro de la ciudad."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:17
translate spanish reba0_467f6397:

    # "I zone out a little, thinking about those times with my dad, how we'd just drive and talk."
    "Me distraigo un poco, pensando en aquellos momentos con mi padre, en cómo conducíamos y hablábamos sin más."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:21
translate spanish reba0_943fdde8:

    # "Then I see a pretty girl standing by an old pickup truck on the side of the road, waving me down."
    "Entonces veo a una chica guapa de pie junto a una vieja camioneta al borde de la carretera, haciéndome señas para que me detuviera."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:22
translate spanish reba0_2d045fa0:

    # "I have a hard time just driving away from a woman in need, so I pull over and park in front of the truck, hoping that I wasn't about to get robbed."
    "Me cuesta mucho alejarme de una mujer que necesita ayuda, así que me detengo y aparco delante de la camioneta, esperando que no me vayan a robar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:23
translate spanish reba0_5501810e:

    # "I step out of the car and walk towards her."
    "Salgo del coche y camino hacia ella."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:27
translate spanish reba0_b5a6a6a3:

    # "Woman" "Oh thank you mister. I was afraid nobody would stop for me."
    "Woman" "Oh, gracias, señor. Temía que nadie se detuviera a ayudarme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:28
translate spanish reba0_6e2d4c28:

    # "Woman" "My truck broke down over here."
    "Woman" "Mi camioneta se ha averiado aquí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:29
translate spanish reba0_adb0ea8c:

    # "Woman" "I'm pretty sure it's the dang battery again. You think I could get a jump off ya?"
    "Woman" "Estoy bastante segura de que es otra vez la maldita batería. ¿Cree que podría darme una mano?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:30
translate spanish reba0_198b50eb:

    # pc "Yeah, I'm sure we could do that. Do you have cables?"
    pc "Sí, claro que podemos hacerlo. ¿Tienes cables?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:31
translate spanish reba0_c821f194:

    # "Woman" "I sure do. If you just turn your car around so that they're front to front, I can take care of the rest."
    "Woman" "Claro que sí. Si das la vuelta al coche para que queden uno frente al otro, yo me encargo del resto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:32
translate spanish reba0_35743d5e:

    # pc "Okay then."
    pc "De acuerdo, entonces."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:35
translate spanish reba0_0f9a51c3:

    # "I do as she said and turn the car around, pulling it close enough that the jumper cables can reach."
    "Hago lo que me dice y doy la vuelta al coche, acercándolo lo suficiente para que los cables de arranque lleguen."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:36
translate spanish reba0_919ef9f8:

    # "Then I pop open the hood and get out to help her with anything that she may need."
    "Luego abro el capó y salgo para ayudarla en lo que necesite."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:37
translate spanish reba0_fb6400d5:

    # "It becomes obvious very quickly that she knows what she is doing and likely knows far more than I do about cars."
    "Enseguida queda claro que sabe lo que hace y que probablemente sabe mucho más que yo de coches."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:38
translate spanish reba0_242be3b5:

    # "After she hooks up the cables, I start the car back up again."
    "Después de que conecta los cables, vuelvo a arrancar el coche."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:42
translate spanish reba0_dd0107cd:

    # "Woman" "We'll just let it sit there for a few minutes, then I bet she'll start right up."
    "Woman" "Vamos a dejarlo ahí unos minutos, seguro que entonces arranca enseguida."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:43
translate spanish reba0_5d38cec5:

    # "Woman" "Thanks again for stopping. Else I might have been stuck here for a while."
    "Woman" "Gracias de nuevo por parar. Si no, me habría quedado tirada aquí un buen rato."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:47
translate spanish reba0_15b8dcea:

    # "Woman" "I left the dang thing at home!"
    "Woman" "¡Me dejé el dichoso aparato en casa!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:48
translate spanish reba0_a4587c6d:

    # "Woman" "Can you believe the rotten luck?"
    "Woman" "¿Te puedes creer la mala suerte que tengo?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:49
translate spanish reba0_712724ea:

    # pc "Oh yeah, that sucks."
    pc "Sí, qué fastidio."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:51
translate spanish reba0_b9dcae90:

    # "Woman" "I know it!"
    "Woman" "¡Ya lo sé!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:52
translate spanish reba0_1d73a536:

    # "Woman" "I never do that, but today when the truck dies, that's the day it happens."
    "Woman" "Nunca hago eso, pero justo hoy, cuando la camioneta se avería, es cuando pasa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:53
translate spanish reba0_6f584abf:

    # "Woman" "Murphy's Law, I reckon."
    "Woman" "La ley de Murphy, supongo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:55
translate spanish reba0_f4441a6d:

    # "Woman" "Yeah, she's my baby."
    "Woman" "Sí, es mi pequeña."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:56
translate spanish reba0_e69dc08e:

    # "Woman" "I spend half my week working on her usually."
    "Woman" "Normalmente me paso la mitad de la semana trabajando en ella."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:57
translate spanish reba0_c6e9f0c6:

    # "Woman" "Takes a lot to keep her running, and even then she ain't gonna be running fast. More just jogging, I reckon."
    "Woman" "Cuesta mucho mantenerla en marcha, y aun así no va a ir rápido. Más bien a paso lento, supongo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:59
translate spanish reba0_aa014be2:

    # "Woman" "It's worth it though. She was my daddy's, you know."
    "Woman" "Pero merece la pena. Era de mi padre, ya sabes."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:60
translate spanish reba0_e246cdd2:

    # "Woman" "He ain't around anymore, but at least I got his truck to remember him by."
    "Woman" "Él ya no está, pero al menos tengo su camioneta para recordarlo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:61
translate spanish reba0_75dc099e:

    # pc "I get it."
    pc "Lo entiendo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:64
translate spanish reba0_406402ca:

    # "Woman" "Well thank you mister, but actually three cars passed me up before you stopped."
    "Woman" "Bueno, gracias, señor, pero en realidad me han adelantado tres coches antes de que usted se detuviera."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:65
translate spanish reba0_178e2dc8:

    # "Woman" "I was thinking I'd have to pop a titty out to get somebody to stop."
    "Woman" "Estaba pensando que tendría que sacar un pecho para que alguien se detuviera."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:66
translate spanish reba0_b9af39c1:

    # pc "Yeah, I bet that'd work. Work for me anyway."
    pc "Sí, apuesto a que eso funcionaría. A mí me funcionaría, al menos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:68
translate spanish reba0_984875f8:

    # "Woman" "I bet it would've!"
    "Woman" "¡Apuesto a que sí!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:70
translate spanish reba0_d587b347:

    # "Woman" "But you stopped without me having to do those things."
    "Woman" "Pero tú paraste sin que tuviera que hacer esas cosas."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:71
translate spanish reba0_98f17ecc:

    # "Woman" "Just 'cause you a nice guy, I reckon."
    "Woman" "Supongo que es porque eres un buen tipo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:72
translate spanish reba0_ff0c3e06:

    # "Woman" "So thank you."
    "Woman" "Así que gracias."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:74
translate spanish reba0_3d45c0c0:

    # "Woman" "What's your name anyway, mister?"
    "Woman" "¿Cómo te llamas, señor?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:75
translate spanish reba0_55be1fd1:

    # pc "[pcname]."
    pc "[pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:76
translate spanish reba0_7e57ae37:

    # rb "Nice to meet ya, [pcname]. I'm Reba Mae Ellis. You can just call me Reba."
    rb "Encantada de conocerte, [pcname]. Soy Reba Mae Ellis. Puedes llamarme Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:77
translate spanish reba0_13791b7c:

    # pc "Nice to meet you, Reba."
    pc "Encantado de conocerte, Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:79
translate spanish reba0_6f72937c:

    # rb "Alright, well let me see if she'll start up now."
    rb "Vale, voy a ver si ahora arranca."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:82
translate spanish reba0_0a5cc5db:

    # "She gets into the truck and turns the key."
    "Se sube a la camioneta y gira la llave."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:83
translate spanish reba0_476ef506:

    # "The engine groans a couple of times before turning over and firing up, the truck rumbling to life."
    "El motor gruñe un par de veces antes de arrancar y ponerse en marcha, y la camioneta cobra vida con un rugido."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:87
translate spanish reba0_205d05b8:

    # rb "That did it!"
    rb "¡Ya está!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:88
translate spanish reba0_f4bc360e:

    # rb "Alternator should charge it up now."
    rb "El alternador debería cargarla ahora."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:90
translate spanish reba0_6f1851b5:

    # rb "I'm pretty sure there's a loose battery cable. Need to get that fixed up some time."
    rb "Estoy bastante seguro de que hay un cable de la batería suelto. Hay que arreglarlo en algún momento."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:91
translate spanish reba0_873a3eaf:

    # rb "Anyway, let me get these cables unhooked and we can both be on our way."
    rb "En fin, déjame desconectar estos cables y así podremos seguir nuestro camino."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:94
translate spanish reba0_4c2431fa:

    # "She bends over into the hood of the truck, displaying her ass in a most pleasing way."
    "Se inclina sobre el capó de la camioneta, mostrando su trasero de una forma muy atractiva."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:95
translate spanish reba0_f6e3fbde:

    # "Those shorts just hug it perfectly, and I get this overwhelming urge to give it a nice smack."
    "Esos pantalones cortos le quedan perfectos, y siento unas ganas irresistibles de darle una buena palmada."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:96
translate spanish reba0_db0e9d91:

    # "I hold back though, and after a few moments, she gets the cable unhooked."
    "Pero me contengo, y al cabo de unos instantes, ella desconecta el cable."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:100
translate spanish reba0_ccdf0335:

    # rb "Thanks again, [pcname]. You really helped me out."
    rb "Gracias de nuevo, [pcname]. Me has ayudado mucho."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:101
translate spanish reba0_ec3e6cf1:

    # pc "I didn't really do much."
    pc "No he hecho gran cosa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:102
translate spanish reba0_02d1df40:

    # rb "Nonsense. You stopped. And you kept me company. I really appreciate it."
    rb "Tonterías. Te has parado. Y me has hecho compañía. Te lo agradezco de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:103
translate spanish reba0_6be08fb5:

    # rb "Here, give me your phone number."
    rb "Toma, dame tu número de teléfono."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:104
translate spanish reba0_2da4129e:

    # "She takes out a pen and hands it to me."
    "Saca un bolígrafo y me lo entrega."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:106
translate spanish reba0_62a89c6e:

    # rb "Just write it down on my arm."
    rb "Escríbelo en mi brazo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:107
translate spanish reba0_7b021782:

    # "I step up close to her and she holds her arm out for me to write my phone number on."
    "Me acerco a ella y me tiende el brazo para que le escriba mi número de teléfono."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:108
translate spanish reba0_813a51bb:

    # rb "I'd just give you my number, but I can't ever remember the dang thing."
    rb "Te daría mi número, pero nunca me acuerdo de esa maldita cosa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:109
translate spanish reba0_0c3f53cd:

    # "I write the number down and give her the pen back."
    "Escribo el número y le devuelvo el bolígrafo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:110
translate spanish reba0_3c2dc917:

    # "Instead of stepping away from me however, she wraps her arms around me."
    "Sin embargo, en lugar de alejarse de mí, me rodea con los brazos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:113
translate spanish reba0_02abc3ae:

    # rb "Thanks so much for helping me out."
    rb "Muchas gracias por ayudarme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:114
translate spanish reba0_f33e2b39:

    # rb "I'll give you a call sometime."
    rb "Te llamaré algún día."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:115
translate spanish reba0_fda5c5fa:

    # rb "Then maybe I'll get a chance to thank you properly."
    rb "Así quizá tenga la oportunidad de darte las gracias como es debido."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:116
translate spanish reba0_152907f3:

    # pc "Uh, okay then."
    pc "Eh, vale, entonces."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:118
translate spanish reba0_fb8bb43d:

    # rb "Alright, [pcname], I better get on home now."
    rb "Muy bien, [pcname], mejor me voy a casa ya."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:119
translate spanish reba0_0ebf6140:

    # rb "I'll talk to you soon, okay?"
    rb "Hablamos pronto, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:120
translate spanish reba0_44cd0ed5:

    # pc "Okay. Nice to meet you, Reba."
    pc "Vale. Encantado de conocerte, Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:121
translate spanish reba0_9aa0d4d9:

    # rb "Nice to meet you too, sweetie."
    rb "Encantada de conocerte también, cariño."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:124
translate spanish reba0_8c3604d7:

    # "With that, she gets back in her truck and I go back to my car and we both drive away in opposite directions."
    "Dicho esto, ella vuelve a su camioneta y yo vuelvo a mi coche, y ambos nos alejamos en direcciones opuestas."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:125
translate spanish reba0_0584fa58:

    # "She seems like a nice girl."
    "Parece una chica agradable."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba0.rpy:126
translate spanish reba0_71610ace:

    # "And that ass. Holy crap, I'd love to see more of that ass."
    "Y ese culo. Joder, me encantaría ver más de ese culo."

